                <h1>Dynamic CSS: Change Text Color by Background</h1>
                <p>Changing text color based on background color in CSS can enhance readability and aesthetics. Use the mix-blend-mode property to dynamically blend text colors with backgrounds. Alternatively, use JavaScript to detect background hues and apply contrasting text colors. This ensures optimal visibility across different designs.</p>
